p.q:
This is my Brethren a very grave and difficult Queſtion; 
                     Anſ. 
                   and to me, conſidering how many places there are wherein the Holy Ghoſt calls upon us to endeavour to be of one mind, of the ſame mind, and of the ſame judgment, it is eaſier to tell you, wherein we may not differ in judgement, and wherein differences in judgement may not be Tolerated, then to tell you wherein they may.

p.note:
Ye receive not the Sacraments (except ſome few) in our Churches but 
                     〈◊〉
                   private meetings,
